snippet.title: Wengie ft. David Amber - Talk Talk (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Watch and listen to "Talk Talk" by Wengie feat. David Amber. Hope you guy's like it, Enjoy! Don't forget to subscribe to my channel for more Your Music Lyrics Updates.

Watch Original video from Wengie here :
 https://youtu.be/6cCo44Pc7Lg

Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/album/5rVTz8...
iTunes: https://music.apple.com/us/album/talk...

Produced by David Amber:
https://instagram.com/davidambersongs 

Follow Wengie 

Join the Music fam!!! http://bit.ly/WengieMusicFam 
Follow me on Spotify: http://bit.ly/WengieSpotify
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/wengie

TALK TALK

LYRICS

Talk, talk, talk
And it's breaking my heart
(All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk)
Shut up!
Talk, talk, talk
And it's breaking my heart
(All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk)
(Hey! Hey!)

You think I can't read your game, oh oh
But I can beat your poker face any day, any day
You're all talk, all words
Let me tell you what I heard
You're always spinnin', sorry
Ooh, I got your number down (oh oh)
No need to put one over cause you're so fire, so fire
You're all talk, sounds, words
Don't believe a single word
Is that all you got for me?

Blah blah blah are the words that you're saying
I didn't wanna know, but now I know I can't go back
Blah blah blah is the sound that I'm hearing
Blah, blah blah, blah
Shut up!

All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey)
Running on your mouth and thinking I'm not onto you
Talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey)
Stop wasting up my time yeah, with your stupid lies (hey!)
I don't need no other, please don't have to bother
Tell me that you never tell the truth, boy
All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (oh, oh, oh)
Talk, talk, talk
And it's breaking my heart

I listen to you run your mouth
Every one else gather round
Let me help you break it down
(Oooh)
Every time I hear you speak
It's like a game of hide and seek
Always lies, never truth
Tell you what you're ought to do
Ooh, I got your number down (oh oh)
No need to put one over cause you're so fire, so fire
You're all talk, sounds, words
Don't believe a single word
Is that all you got for me

Blah blah blah are the words that you're saying
I didn't wanna know, but now I know I can't go back
Blah blah blah is the sound that I'm hearing
Blah, blah blah, blah (oh, woah)
Shut up!

All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey)
Running on your mouth and thinking I'm not onto you
Talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey)
Stop wasting up my time yeah, with your stupid lies (hey!)
I don't need no other, please don't have to bother
Tell me that you never tell the truth, boy
All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (oh, oh, oh)
Talk, talk, talk
And it's breaking my heart

Now I don't wanna hear it
I want you off my mind
(Oh oh, oh oh)
No, I don't really need this
I need someone to believe in

How bout you shut it, shut it up?
Shut it up, shut it up?
How bout you shut it, shut it up?
Shut it up, shut it up?
How bout you shut it, shut it up?
Shut it up, shut it up?
Blah, blah blah, blah
(Yeah!)

All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey)
Running on your mouth and thinking I'm not onto you
Talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey)
Stop wasting up my time yeah, with your stupid lies
I don't need no other, please don't have to bother
Tell me that you never tell the truth, boy
All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (oh, oh, oh)
Talk, talk, talk
And it's breaking my heart

Running it up, running it up, your mouth
(Talk, talk, talk, talk, hey!)
Running it up, running it up, your mouth
(Talk, talk, talk, talk, hey!)
Running it up, running it up, your mouth
(Yeah)
All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk

Talk, talk, talk
And it's (breaking my heart)

Wendy Ayche (Chinese: 黃文洁), better known as Wengie, is a Chinese Australian YouTuberpersonality, vlogger, singer, and voice actress. As of 2018, her YouTube channel had over 13 million subscribers, making her the most popular YouTuber from Australia. Her channel was the 6th most subscribed "how-to and style" channel on YouTube, as of January 2018.

Artist: Wengie
Featured artist: David Amber
Released: 2019
Genre: Pop
